\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tool</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>웹 프론트엔드: HTML, CSS, JS</li>\n<li>Open API: 카카오맵 API</li>\n<li>서버&#x26;벡엔드: Nginx + Express.js: Rest API</li>\n<li>데이터베이스: MySQL, DB설계와 SQL</li>\n<li>클라우드: AWS EC2 + Ubuntu</li>\n<li>Git &#x26; Github</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"url\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#url\" aria-label=\"url permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>URL</h3>\n<p>🛠 카카오 Map API</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href = \"https://apis.map.kakao.com/\"><a href=\"https://apis.map.kakao.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://apis.map.kakao.com/</a></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Youtube channel</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href = \"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHw5u2NzzRCZ15C-npOOefw\">클론코딩 참고 채널 - 동네코딩</a></li>\n<li><a href = \"https://youtu.be/b11HnycEgVg\">웹 프로젝트 영상</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#-%EC%B9%B4%EC%B9%B4%EC%98%A4-%EB%A7%B5api%EB%A5%BC-%ED%99%9C%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%9C-%ED%95%99%EA%B5%90-%EC%A3%BC%EB%B3%80-%EB%A7%9B%EC%A7%91-%EC%A7%80%EB%8F%84\">📕 카카오 맵API를 활용한 학교 주변 맛집 지도</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\